    <h1>About us</h1>
    <div class="description">_____________________________________________<br><br>
      Baz'art is a platform that showcases the beauty of authentic handmade products from Morocco. It was founded with the goal of providing a global stage for artisans and their creations, emphasizing the cultural narrative behind each handmade piece. The platform celebrates the fusion of tradition and innovation and offers a diverse range of products including metalwork, pottery, leather, and furniture.<br><br>
      Every product on Baz'art has its own unique story, reflecting the company's commitment to quality, authenticity, and timeless beauty. They believe that each handmade creation carries the essence of Moroccan craftsmanship and aims to make every purchase an opportunity to connect with the heart and soul of this rich tradition. By bringing these meaningful objects into your home, you can create a living canvas that embodies the spirit of Moroccan craftsmanship.<br><br>
    </div>
    <h2 class="welcome">Welcome to Baz'art, where the beauty of handmade products is celebrated and cherished.</h2>
